{"tid":2376512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 咁岩係油麻地叫緊雞 點同老婆交代???!!","createTime":"2021-01-23T00:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T06:34:21.000Z","uid":120847,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c97a242f8f953f36e94d84b70e313960b5a9363f","tid":2376512,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T00:56:23.000Z","msg":"琴晚玩緊毒龍鑽嘅時候突然有幾十架警車出現係樓下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後有人用大聲公叫上黎「樓上嘅住客，根據預防及控制疾病規例599J，你身處嘅位置已經成為封鎖範圍，請你放低武器，留係住所直到檢測完畢!」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即刻嚇到鳩都縮，囡囡見我鳩縮於是條脷愈鑽愈入，好似採緊鼻咽式子咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我都係射了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加點算好 我同隻雞係一樓一你眼望我眼<br />\n<br />\n佢仲話要當我加鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33d46524a094628493c143ac84fce72cb2f336e","tid":2376512,"uid":120916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T01:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34912e0605d203a7fc348a7176c6f9836ae33b61","tid":2376512,"uid":186431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T01:03:47.000Z","msg":"後樓梯跳落去跑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e01256be2af54c5ba70ba7b2b8dd7327833e124","tid":2376512,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T01:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89859e73d456b19e9c539576b73827b176dda849","tid":2376512,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T01:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e9a548f1d57a